  "texts": [
    "Table 4 shows some interesting examples of the response.",
    "It is clear that GPT2 often generated generic or irrelevant responses.",
    "Even when answering questions about side effects (Question 5), it described generic side effects like \"feeling weak and tired\" which was not very specific to the treatment in question.",
    "BioGPT does not suffer from this problem.",
    "Its answers were mostly related to the question even when it failed to produce the correct answer."
